{"tid":1480334,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"會唔會有人想學韓文?","createTime":"2019-08-17T09:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T05:11:06.000Z","uid":10310,"like":3,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3f6ff1fcf2460a21a37c674235280e775c6ec2f1","tid":1480334,"uid":10310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:11:04.000Z","msg":"眼見好多教韓/日文既中心都食水好深<br />\n淨係教個發音都教4堂 然後一本書又加你4次錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n進度又慢 錢又係咁加 學完出黎感覺到自己又好似未係點溝通到咁<br />\n所以我同我朋友決定出黎教教韓日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(其實都係夾返租錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />先講講我自己先 我自己就學左韓文都6-7年了 咩大型中心私補都去過 亦係大學主修過韓文 韓國文化都略知一二 考到宜家Topik level5<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦都有做左2年韓文私補<br />\n另外我朋友就N1 係日本有留過學 對於日本文化都有一定認識<br />\n好有心想向大家交流下學日文心得<br />\n<br />\n我地好有心想著重多D係口語方面 文法係緊要 但語言學黎都係要為溝通<br />\n所以好想各位巴絲學完起碼可以同日本/韓國人溝通到先<br />\n另一方面都會重視文法 好讓大家可以可以考級黎証明自己實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間: 初級班暫定係星期六 2:00pm-3:30pm<br />\n地點:喺旺角book課室<br />\n價錢:會因程度而定<br />\n<br />\n另外更設有私人1對1班 方便要返shift或者時間唔穩定/想進度快一D既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣嘅巴打絲打就快啲填Google form啦！<br />\n日文:<a href=\"https://forms.gle/6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2F6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=b8ff0022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/6GNy2L2ZDrsz9gmh9</a><br />\n韓文:<a href=\"https://forms.gle/YQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FYQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8&d=9fV5YN%2BdLeg0vJDpI0pnmjMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=bff2052e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/YQ8zwEHitfPF8TfA8</a>"},{"pid":"485c3b4ad496001986f0160443d272d5e91ef58b","tid":1480334,"uid":260312,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T09:14:19.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"607e047f7e2a35138fda93bbae973e199748934b","tid":1480334,"uid":10310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:22:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"90a56ee8c5ef1b71a616ea823b1fed02668e9e80","tid":1480334,"uid":238301,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"寵寵 寵寵寵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"772d9ac4bb2f025652529ebf53164694a467b148","tid":1480334,"uid":296307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"想學 但旺角唔就腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80fcdfcc7f33fb252d716f694760402689552e7f","tid":1480334,"uid":10310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"772d9ac4bb2f025652529ebf53164694a467b148","tid":1480334,"uid":296307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"想學 但旺角唔就腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:40:48.000Z","msg":"可以墳左表先 再傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f6009ca23c9b8551704626f710d8f356649368","tid":1480334,"uid":188132,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"咁既時勢唔好係度搵食啦 好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e535733b0604bf6a1b262065dbe5fa5f02f8d49c","tid":1480334,"uid":10310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d5dbad5f49626f556a52f6a0f7ed6bc669d3d77e","tid":1480334,"uid":10310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:57:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ee797edecb2be1ba11f80708ae317d0b4cfcbf91","tid":1480334,"uid":10310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pi